Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. You know what I do for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really expect me to spill everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} should know what I do for a living, Leroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In 1944, the Japanese army dug an underground\Nshelter here in preparation for attrition warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That should make a safe hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you kill Leroy for this information?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't kill information brokers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I buy information with money.\NI put it all on Young Master's tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only reminded him that the maid probably paid him too little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, where is Roberta?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.69,0:02:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caxton.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Will!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you have some bad news for us, Will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's going on. I sent out a zone recon squad just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. We've been detecting wiretap noise on the phone for a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the latest local situation report and the modified operation plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Brigadier General Wilder. The operation will continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue your reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roads to Charkuan and Manthai Streets are closed to traffic due to construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no actual construction is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Street vendors and prostitutes have completely disappeared from the vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were approximately nine lookouts and four tailers within the 200-yard radius to the outskirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. We will conduct street cleanup operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will, you'd best escape before the bullets start flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in formation in front of the hotel that Abrego told us about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The U.S. Army, FARC commandos, not to mention the mercenaries the maid got from this town—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a huge free-for-all lies ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.53,0:03:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not make it, but I'll get more people!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, the phone's been ringing for ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:04:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Shenhua! Time to make some money. You'll get to kill a lot of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could chop ya up for free anytime, ya know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your boss that got me into this, so don't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time it's commissioned by a certain super wealthy South American.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That... how much?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Charlie to Alpha. Current situation Dog Four.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An apparently armed group is headed to your direction. Precaution is advised.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Charlie. Bravo and Charlie, prepare to move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't quite understand what we got ourselves into,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it'll put an end to this boring standby period.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, time for action, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is D1.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An armed group is entering the target building.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Locate the Bloodhound. Our only target is Rosarita Cisneros.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that some country mafia took refuge here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On this second floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leroy's information is always accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counting down. Three, two, one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cease fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll detonate the claymores. Everyone take cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the guys who went upstairs are dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing? We're going up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck! What happened up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's in the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone! The wall, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shane, there's an enemy on the building\Nto the rear, on top of the tallest billboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone take cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, who exactly are we facing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wright! Horner! Suppression fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Others, move out quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:06:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest of you, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're totally late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, the gunfire game is on, vintage-style!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a full-out war! We're charging ya extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're still fighting, then the chief must be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garcia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch told me to withdraw here, multiple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you want to see this\Nthrough to the end, I will join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Roberta is waiting, then I have to go greet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well said. That's the chivalric spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target located on the rooftop of the\Nrear building. We'll send a squad around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garcia, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not now. Open it when you can't figure out what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's only good for sitting on a bench in the sun\Nwith canned coffee. Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master is no different...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost your virginity at the bar, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first time shooting people, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wield shotguns and grenades.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone can tell you can't really aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the trick. Just think of them as signboards,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nothing more than rusty, corroded signboards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep that in mind as you live on,\Nyou'll be a full-fledged gunslinger one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to be like you—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gunshots ceased. This is D1. Engaging the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've cornered the enemy on the rooftop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no good! Our cover is useless!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D3, go reinforce.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, the Bloodhound is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's pursuing something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It must be the unidentified group ahead of us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merge with D3. Pursue the Bloodhound together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can never trust those racketeers from the cartel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those shots are official U.S. Army carbines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! We're merging with D3!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shenhua, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are out-of-range shots from a Barrett rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've cornered ourselves in the enemy's field, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn it. They're all dead and useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have held back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any guy here that's at least {\i1}half{\i0} alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy? Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, beaner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't be rough. He's almost dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Translate for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Where's Roberta? Tell me and\NI'll take you to the doctor." Tell him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0170,,We won't hurt you. Where's Rosarita?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0170,,We just want to know where Rosarita went.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0170,,Tell us and we'll take you to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0170,,Rosarita went after someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0170,,and is headed to the intersection to the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0170,,Am I going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0170,,Worry not. God will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chief maid is headed to the intersection to the west after the U.S. Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The west? All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beaner, does it hurt? Let me treat you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the intersection at Lansup Street and Nankwai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head there for now. We've got no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fabiola!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. You're pointing the dangerous end of the gun at me. What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The match was decided. What the fuck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The match only ends after the final blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that true for your barrios, too? Isn't it the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he sincerely sought relief at the verge of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you shot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you've done is {\i1}aniquilación{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak English, {\i1}chiquita{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She meant an annihilation, Miss Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You enjoy shooting people, just like Jeffrey Murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dahmer", you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little maid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More moral lessons? Then we'll just cut our way through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. We have yet to catch up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Young Master makes the smart choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawyer, lead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone does the dance of death in this corrupt town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we need the professional troubleshooters...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that is, those ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's precisely why you should act\Nas you believe is right, Fabiola.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we will all return together, back to our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will all return home together. That's why we are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will Garcia catch up to Roberta? Hard to say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In any case, the U.S. Army has no room for escape now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is virtually impossible for them\Nto shake off the Bloodhound of Florencia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to complete the formation to let the U.S. Army escape.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To do so, I must wait for yet another syndicate that dwells in this town to join the scene.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you were too late, Rock.\NI can see the fireworks all the way from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't need you calling me right now, damn it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close it up. Dutch could get mad any time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Chang, I cannot do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The actors are still on stage—both the boy and the maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't exit from the backstage now. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what? You said you could get a checkmate in this game of chess, and I bet on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was enough. Now that the situation has turned out this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what's the point in holding concern for the boy or the maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rock, what I hate the most in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is hypocrisy. That is more evil than an evil deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a poison that deceives not only others but also the self.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may smell like a rose, but you can't hide the fact that shit is still shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you already know, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For both me and, as of now, you,\Nthe Young Master of Loveless and his maid...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}are mere pawns on our chessboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Chang, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one cruel son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! I haven't heard something like that for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I like that personality of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your rage is due to, first, being too\Nstubborn to give up a losing game,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and second, because I managed to sum up your innermost thoughts so succinctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the past, I had to venture into people's\Nminds far deeper than you ever did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can you, a gangster living in violence, speak for a person's mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The man talking to you right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once passionately upheld the worthless sense\Nof justice alongside the Hong Kong police,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fighting as a guardian of law and order.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A life of hypocrisy isn't too uncommon in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should realize you're just another chess piece and step back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the best for the sake of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let it end just yet, Mr. Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then do what you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:17:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, after this biting conversation we've just had,\NI'll be expecting a pretty bold and daring game play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pursuit section D2. Target spotted one block ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Approach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are we still going for it? The only ones left are—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it, Jose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our friends' deaths will be in vain if we withdraw here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain. Should I just ask them to let us pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to get rid of whoever's in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not mind breaking through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have one question for you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? So you can actually speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that high stand. Showing up from there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,might look cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what did you bring him along for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind him. He's just a poor little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gunshots aren't ceasing.\NWho's rallying with whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll let the enemy pass by and have a diversionary squad follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the meantime, we will coordinate with Bravo and Charlie for a pincer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, check your bullets. Hold onto your magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What comes after this operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find a hideout in the outskirts and wait for NSA's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, focus on capturing and annihilating the enemy at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hope she falls right into our trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right. We took your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chief is on the other side of this scramble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is D4. Hurrying to support D2. Now combat—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, run to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make it through if you're alone. Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is clear tonight, and the moon azure,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet, poor wretches, your wicked weapons aim at the littlest lambs!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This favorite gun of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,crushes every enemy it hits to a million pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lord is present, yet He merely watches from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who else but I can deliver in His name the—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fabiola!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:20:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot cross over there, so please hide somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Hurry up, Fabiola!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D4 was held back by another enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not our true enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I would go for a pincer if I were\Ncommanding the U.S. army troops."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's the U.S. army's strategy." That's what we told Rosarita.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the Bloodhound's position must be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fabiola?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still firing at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fabiola...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.47,0:22:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Central nervous system stimulant...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the drug Roberta ordered from Doctor Hartland!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Communication with Lohes was cut off on the third floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we found her. She's right upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roberta is here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll finally catch up with her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.60,0:23:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lohes, anything unusual on the third floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong, Lohes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I can still make it. Roberta will never lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't lose! I believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.49,0:23:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your skills are still up to par, Bloodhound.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.60,0:24:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.28,0:24:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single move you know, I know as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am from Havana.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.19,0:24:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cuban Special Naval Missions Formation...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely. I'm here on FARC Comandante Marulanda's direct orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.31,0:24:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be thinking "Why don't you shoot?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.86,0:24:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had many chances to shoot you had I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.17,0:24:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The commander intends to kill you by\Nall means necessary, but I think otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.87,0:24:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the activist that drew the most attention\Nat the South American guerrilla meetings back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.09,0:24:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the only one who deserved to\Ninherit the title of Jackal after old Carlos.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.68,0:25:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any organization is in absolute need of such a talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.16,0:25:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return with me, Bloodhound.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.55,0:25:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you remain a maid in a countryside mansion, you cannot resist the smell of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.54,0:25:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.84,0:25:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a boring place that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.45,0:25:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with neither blood nor gunshots.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.46,0:25:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master's death was a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.76,0:25:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My obligation ends once I take revenge upon the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.85,0:25:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make the right choice, Rosarita.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.84,0:25:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost finished, so don't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.43,0:25:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.24,0:25:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Americans' heads would make great gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.57,0:25:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt the Comandante will forgive me so readily.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.32,0:25:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me. All of Havana follows my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.15,0:25:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The FARC cannot dare reject it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.00,0:26:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.09,0:26:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.84,0:26:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering what could come after this, would it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.21,0:26:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wise of me to befriend you in advance?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.59,0:26:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pursuing the U.S. troops would come first.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.26,0:26:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't move until I leave here and follow their decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.41,0:26:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this place is just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.98,0:26:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a greenhouse warmed up by the heat of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.32,0:26:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It turns me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.73,0:26:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bloodhound, are you testing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.29,0:26:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the one doing the testing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.61,0:26:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you my dog? Stick out your tongue like a dog if you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.94,0:27:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't rip it apart. I don't want to fight the Americans naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.14,0:27:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you strip my bottom for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.86,0:27:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous. Do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.29,0:27:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are careful. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.67,0:27:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pull it down slowly, so don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.40,0:27:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.16,0:27:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.26,0:27:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have been even more, more, far more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.48,0:28:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never join hands with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.97,0:28:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because both you and those foxes serve the same master:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.12,0:28:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,doctrines and ideals!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.84,0:28:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never serve under that swindler again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.38,0:28:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one man in this world who can collar me:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.29,0:28:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garcia Fernando Lovelace, the master I chose for myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.91,0:28:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the unique being that I will eat dirt\Nand sacrifice my life to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.36,0:28:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only for his sake will I pursue and kill the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.77,0:28:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will bite to death even my own kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.92,0:28:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not a bloodhound.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.78,0:28:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a diseased stray wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.11,0:29:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roberta, stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.34,0:29:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, stop it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.59,0:29:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, stop... stop...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.92,0:29:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.59,0:29:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Young... Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.57,0:29:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.38,0:29:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Young Master! Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.93,0:29:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.03,0:29:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.37,0:29:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.13,0:29:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.51,0:29:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, Young Master!\NWhat should I do? What should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.65,0:30:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you keep envisioning me\Nto avoid this from happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.86,0:30:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just... Just when will you stop following me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.67,0:30:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.07,0:30:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not quite. It's you who isn't forgetting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.42,0:30:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you assaulted the Magdalena branch of Taisho Electric\Nand shot two Japanese engineers to death—
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.30,0:30:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yes, it has already been seven years—
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.81,0:30:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you ripped apart my family photo before killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.55,0:30:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That remained within you as one of your numerous little emotional wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.92,0:30:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the wounds hopelessly festered and gangrened amid the calm, peaceful daily life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.19,0:30:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had you remained with that boy,\Nthose wounds may have healed someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.56,0:30:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it was you who ruined that chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.05,0:30:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what should I have done to be forgiven?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.90,0:31:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could never be forgiven,\Nhow could I show my face in that mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.26,0:31:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've kept following me like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.52,0:31:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that I cannot forget, so that I can never forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.75,0:31:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did you take my late Master as a sacrifice, but Young Master is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.40,0:31:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.03,0:31:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.64,0:31:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're showing this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.96,0:31:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to destroy me that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.07,0:31:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Young Master can't possibly be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.71,0:31:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master is waiting in the garden for me to return with the heads of the conniving foxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.76,0:31:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master will greet me with a smile, and everything will be back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.68,0:31:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you showed me this horrible vision of Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.90,0:32:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You showed me the last thing I'd want to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.12,0:32:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.19,0:32:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This here is not Young Master,\Nbut rather an illusion just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.55,0:32:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will prove it here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.41,0:32:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Burrows.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.53,0:32:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Met target in building on patrol. Used tear-gas bomb.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.64,0:32:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sergeant Major Horner secured a boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.71,0:32:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Sergeant Major Horner.\NCeasing tactical diversion. We will return to point!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.68,0:32:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.17,0:33:49.17,NextEp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,900)\blur10}NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.34,0:33:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rock, you told me to read this when I feel lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.53,0:33:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.95,0:34:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand who exactly I'm dealing with?
